Bobertron grinned as he walked into magmatron's new
base. He saw magmatron emerge from the shadows. He was
bigger now and had a three beast fuzor beast mode!
This was very interesting. But of course bobertron had
more important things to do. Out of his pocket he
pulled out a golden key. It had the symbol of the
autobots embeded on it. Magamatron grinned at the
sight. When they stole the golden disc unaware to
megatron he had also stolen the key to the Ark. This
being the only way the ark would ever fly again. This
could be a useful tool in the war.
